---
const paypalDonateUrl =
  "https://www.paypal.com/donate/?hosted_button_id=77MXKAB84XP8L";
---

<dialog
  id="donation-modal"
  class="donation-modal"
  aria-labelledby="donation-modal-title"
>
  <div class="donation-modal-backdrop" data-donation-modal-close></div>
  <div class="donation-modal-inner">
    <button
      type="button"
      id="donation-modal-close"
      class="donation-modal-close"
      aria-label="Chiudi finestra donazione"
    >
      ×
    </button>
    <p id="donation-modal-title" class="donation-modal-title">
      Ti rubo solo un minuto
    </p>
    <p>
      Mantengo questo sito <b>senza pubblicità</b> perché preferisco che rimanga pulito,
      veloce e piacevole da usare per tutti. Ogni giorno riceve molti visitatori e
      questo mi fa davvero piacere, ma allo stesso tempo comporta anche <b
        >costi di gestione</b
      > (server, manutenzione, aggiornamenti).
    </p>
    <p>
      Per questo motivo ho deciso di aggiungere la possibilità di fare una
      <b>donazione tramite PayPal</b>. Non è assolutamente obbligatorio, ma se
      il sito ti è utile e vuoi contribuire a mantenerlo online e senza
      pubblicità, anche un piccolo contributo può fare la differenza.
    </p>
    <p>Grazie di cuore a chi deciderà di supportare il progetto.</p>
    <div class="donation-modal-actions">
      <a href={paypalDonateUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 154.728 190.5">
          <path
            fill="#001c64"
            d="M60.529 38.103a5.49 5.49 0 0 0-5.423 4.633l-9.013 57.15-8.281 52.514-.005.044.01-.044 8.281-52.514c.421-2.669 2.719-4.633 5.42-4.633h26.404c26.573 0 49.127-19.387 53.246-45.658.314-1.996.482-3.973.52-5.924v-.003h-.003c-6.753-3.543-14.683-5.565-23.372-5.565z"
          ></path>
          <path
            fill="#0070e0"
            d="M131.686 43.669c-.037 1.951-.207 3.93-.52 5.926-4.119 26.271-26.673 45.658-53.246 45.658H51.516c-2.701 0-4.999 1.964-5.42 4.633L37.815 152.4l-5.197 32.947a4.46 4.46 0 0 0 4.405 5.153h28.66a5.49 5.49 0 0 0 5.423-4.633l7.55-47.881c.423-2.669 2.722-4.636 5.423-4.636h16.876c26.573 0 49.124-19.386 53.243-45.655 2.924-18.649-6.46-35.614-22.511-44.026z"
          ></path>
          <path
            fill="#003087"
            d="M27.967 0a5.49 5.49 0 0 0-5.423 4.636L.055 147.244A4.46 4.46 0 0 0 4.46 152.4h33.351l8.281-52.514 9.013-57.15a5.49 5.49 0 0 1 5.423-4.633h47.782c8.691 0 16.621 2.025 23.375 5.563C132.145 19.749 112.41 0 85.273 0z"
          ></path>
        </svg> Dona con PayPal</a
      >
      <button
        type="button"
        id="donation-modal-no-thanks"
        class="donation-modal-no-thanks"
      >
        <b>No grazie</b>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>

<style>
  .donation-modal {
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: transparent;
    max-width: none;
    max-height: none;
    width: min(70ch, calc(100vw - 2rem));
    margin: auto;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .donation-modal::backdrop {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
  }

  .donation-modal[open] .donation-modal-inner {
    animation: donation-modal-enter 0.3s ease-out;
  }

  .donation-modal-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .donation-modal-backdrop {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
  }

  .donation-modal-inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    background: #ffc439;
    color: #111111;
    border: 1px solid #111111;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    z-index: 1;
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  @keyframes donation-modal-enter {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translate3d(0, 2.5rem, 0);
    }

    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    }
  }

  .donation-modal-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1.5rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .donation-modal-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .donation-modal-actions a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .donation-modal-actions a svg {
    height: 1rem;
  }

  .donation-modal-no-thanks {
    border: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    cursor: pointer;
    font: inherit;
  }

  .donation-modal-no-thanks:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .donation-modal p {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .donation-modal :global(.btn) {
    background: #111111;
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #111111;
  }

  .donation-modal :global(.btn:hover) {
    background: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .donation-modal a:not(.btn) {
    color: #111111;
    text-decoration-color: #111111;
  }

  @media screen and (width > 60rem) {
    .donation-modal-inner {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<style is:global>
  body.donation-modal-open {
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-right: var(--donation-modal-scrollbar-width, 0);
  }
</style>

<script>
  const modal = document.getElementById("donation-modal");
  const closeBtn = document.getElementById("donation-modal-close");
  const noThanksBtn = document.getElementById("donation-modal-no-thanks");
  const backdrop = modal?.querySelector("[data-donation-modal-close]");
  const body = document.body;

  const lockPageScroll = () => {
    const scrollbarWidth =
      window.innerWidth - document.documentElement.clientWidth;
    body.style.setProperty(
      "--donation-modal-scrollbar-width",
      `${Math.max(scrollbarWidth, 0)}px`,
    );
    body.classList.add("donation-modal-open");
  };

  const unlockPageScroll = () => {
    body.classList.remove("donation-modal-open");
    body.style.removeProperty("--donation-modal-scrollbar-width");
  };

  const closeModal = () => {
    if (!(modal instanceof HTMLDialogElement)) return;
    modal.close();
    unlockPageScroll();
  };

  const openModal = () => {
    if (!(modal instanceof HTMLDialogElement) || modal.open) return;
    lockPageScroll();
    modal.showModal();
  };

  document.addEventListener("donation-modal:open", openModal);
  closeBtn?.addEventListener("click", closeModal);
  noThanksBtn?.addEventListener("click", closeModal);
  backdrop?.addEventListener("click", closeModal);
  modal?.addEventListener("cancel", (event) => {
    event.preventDefault();
    closeModal();
  });
  modal?.addEventListener("close", unlockPageScroll);
</script>
